==Tailoring==
Milk is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the [[Tailoring|White Overalls Shirt]]. [[File:Shirt071.png|24px]]

==Quests==
*Milk may be randomly requested during any season at the [[Quests#Help Wanted Quests|"Help Wanted" board]] outside [[Pierre's General Store]] for a reward of {{Price|375}} and 150 [[Friendship]] points.  Milk will never be requested unless you own a [[Cow]] or [[Goat]]. (Owning a goat will result in cow's milk being requested.)

==History==
{{History|1.0|Introduced.}}
{{History|1.1|Increased value from 100g to 125g}}
{{History|1.3.27|Made all recipes that use milk accept large milk, not just regular milk.}}
{{History|1.4|Can now be used in [[Tailoring]].}}
{{History|1.5|Made all recipes that use milk accept goat milk or large goat milk.}}

